Package: vc-wifitracker
Version: 1.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.7), tcpdump
Maintainer: VC Team <info@vc-wifitracker.local>
Description: VC WiFi Tracking Service
 Monitors nearby WiFi access points by capturing beacon frames
 with tcpdump. Extracts BSSID, signal strength, channel, and
 ESSID information. Runs as a systemd service.
